                </span>
                Tinatapi
                <small>An API that provides information useful to travellers</small>
            </h1>
            <p class="lead">
                This API uses data from UK Foreign &amp; Commonwealth Office and other sources.
            </p>
            <p>
                This submission for <a href="https://twitter.com/search?q=FCOHACK">#FCOHACK</a> brings together different FCO (& external) datasets to make them more accessible.
            </p>
            <p>
                <i class="fa fa-lg fa-github"></i> It is <strong>public domain</strong> software and lives at <a href="https://github.com/iaincollins/fcohack2014">https://github.com/iaincollins/fcohack2014</a>
            </p>
            <h2>API URLs</h2>
            <hr/>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    <p><a href="/country/">/country/</a> - Get information about all available countries.</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p><a href="/country/UK">/country/{2 ISO}</a> - Get information about a specific country using it's 2 character ISO code.</p>
                    <p>Examples:</p>
                    <p><a href="/country/US">/country/US</a> - United States</p>
                    <p><a href="/country/AF">/country/AF</a> - Afghanistan</p>
                    <p><a href="/country/ZW">/country/ZW</a> - Zimbabwe</p>
                    <p><a href="/country/IR">/country/IR</a> - Iran</p>
                </li>
            </ul>
